            short_text: "Why Book KLIA Express Tickets Online?",
            long_text: "KLIA Express is a fast and easily accessible train service from the Kuala Lumpur International Airport to KL Sentral in the city or back. This Kuala Lumpur Airport Transfer will ensure an efficient and super punctual train connection and is your best bet to get to the airport or the city in the fastest manner. KLIA Express is greatly sought after owing to its speed and quality services.",
