            home_title_367: "Combo (Save 7%): Underwater World + Langkawi Cable Car Tickets",  
            ticket_797: "With these combo tickets to the Underwater World and Langkawi Cable Car ride, get the best of this island city, while you save money.",  
            ticket_798: "Manifest a scene straight out of a nature documentary, but you're right in the middle of it! Visit Underwater World to witness 4,000 incredible marine life from across the globe.",  
            ticket_799: "Find out what it's like to walk on the ocean beds in the 15m-long tunnel and see sharks, giant stingrays, and green turtles gliding overhead.",  
            ticket_800: "Ride the highest cable car in all of Malaysia, giving you idyllic views of Langkawi island while floating 708 meters above sea level",  
            home_title_368: "Combo (Save 33%): Dream Forest Langkawi + Langkawi Underwater World Tickets",  
            ticket_801: "Double the delight as you explore two of Langkawi's top attractions, Dream Forest Langkawi and Langkawi Underwater World, with this discounted combo.",  
