            main_h1text14: "",

            main_ptext2: "KLIA Express plies along the Kuala Lumpur Airport - KL Sentral route. A distance of 60 km is covered in mere 30 minutes by KLIA Express, making it extremely popular with tourists for a time efficient commute. KLIA Express stops at both the airport terminals and seamlessly connects to a pivotal transit hub and commercial center in the city - KL Sentral.",
