            main_ptext4: "Kuala Lumpur Sentral, 50470 Kuala Lumpur, Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia",
            main_ptext5: "Catch up on work or stay connected with the free wifi onboard KLIA Express.",
            main_ptext6: "Simply scan your QR code for entry into the train and enjoy a seamless experience with KLIA Express.",
            main_ptext7: "Stay cool and comfortable in the air-conditioned train coaches.",
