            main_ptext10: "Be entertained with the digital infotainment present onboard.",
            main_ptext11: "It is highly advisable to book online as it lets you avoid queues and enjoy the best ticket deals, thereby saving time and money.",
            main_ptext12: "Connecting from KL Sentral is extremely straightforward as KL Sentral is a well-linked transit hub with many trains, buses, taxis and car rentals available.",
